org.keycloak.models.cache

Interface CachedUserModel.Streams

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CachedUserModel, RoleMapperModel, RoleMapperModel.Streams, UserModel, UserModel.Streams
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserAdapter
    Enclosing interface:
    CachedUserModel

    public static interface CachedUserModel.Streams
extends CachedUserModel, UserModel.Streams
    The CachedUserModel.Streams interface differs from CachedUserModel in that it extends the UserModel.Streams interface, allowing implementations of CachedUserModel to focus on the Stream-based methods in the UserModel interface.
